OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779098804
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 65-year-
OL,4,Cold woman found dead at Sussex home
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a woman in
OL,8,FDurrington.
OL,10,FPolice were called to an address in
OL,11,FDurrington Lane, Worthing at about
OL,12,F7.50pm on Thursday, 14 May, following
OL,13,Fconcerns for the welfare of a woman.
OL,15,FEmergency services attended the scene,
OL,16,Fwhere they found the body of a 65-year-
OL,17,Fold woman.
OL,19,FA 37-year-old man was arrested on
OL,20,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
