PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779098804
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 65-year-
OL,4,Cold woman found dead at Sussex home
OL,6,FAlexandru Nechifor, 37, of Durrington
OL,7,FLane, Worthing has now been charged
OL,8,Fwith murder and two counts of
OL,9,Fassaulting a police constable in the
OL,10,Fexecution of his or her duty.
OL,12,FHe remains in custody ahead of his
OL,13,Fnext court appearance at Worthing
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Monday 18 May.
OL,16,FEnquiries are ongoing and it has been
OL,17,Festablished that the victim and
OL,18,Fsuspect were known to each other.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
