PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1779098804
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after 65-year-
OL,4,Cold woman found dead at Sussex home
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Amanda Zinyama,
OL,7,Ffrom the Major Crime Team, said: "This
OL,8,Fremains fast moving investigation and
OL,9,Four thoughts continue to be with the
OL,10,Fwoman's loved ones at this extremely
OL,11,Fdifficult time.
OL,13,FWe understand this incident will have
OL,14,Fcaused concern in the local community;
OL,15,Fhowever, we continue to believe it to
OL,16,Fbe an isolated incident and we are not
OL,17,Flooking for anyone else in connection
OL,18,Fwith the investigation."
